  {
    "name": "searchStays",
    "title": "Search Stays",
    "description": "Search accommodations (hotels, pensions, resorts, etc.) on MyRealTrip(마이리얼트립). Keywords: 숙소, 호텔, 펜션, 리조트, hotel, accommodation, stay, lodging. Supports filters for price, sorting, and amenities. ⚠️ Returns only listing summaries (name, price range, rating). Does NOT include room types, per-room pricing, amenities, or reviews. When user asks about specific hotel details, room types (룸 타입/객실), room prices (객실 가격), facilities, or uses keywords like '자세히/상세/detail', you MUST follow up with getStayDetail using the gid from these results.",
